Reasoning: The paper discusses the development of a deep learning-based image recognition system for food items, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of smart devices and the deployment of the system as an API service also suggest the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a corpus of food images, indicating the involvement of information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
